{"tid":2241313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國最新失業率升至4.5%　高於市場預期","createTime":"2020-10-13T08:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:09:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60cea51af11f116729fe3df3cf3f4f54a2bf257e","tid":2241313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554492-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554492-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=38c1b2c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554492-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd11e9fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554492-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國的數據顯示，截至8月的3個月失業率升至4.5%，高於5至7月的4.1%，亦超出市場預期的4.3%。期內就業人數減少15.3萬人，減幅遠超出市場預期的3萬人。<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行早前預期，至今年底失業率將觸及7.5%，因政府縮減500億英鎊就業保障計劃，並在11月以一個規模相對較小的計劃所取代。"},{"pid":"f185f05db311aa7088ef777d110cae16172c9ad2","tid":2241313,"uid":279819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60cea51af11f116729fe3df3cf3f4f54a2bf257e","tid":2241313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554492-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554492-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=38c1b2c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554492-20201013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd11e9fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554492-20201013.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國的數據顯示，截至8月的3個月失業率升至4.5%，高於5至7月的4.1%，亦超出市場預期的4.3%。期內就業人數減少15.3萬人，減幅遠超出市場預期的3萬人。<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行早前預期，至今年底失業率將觸及7.5%，因政府縮減500億英鎊就業保障計劃，並在11月以一個規模相對較小的計劃所取代。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"咁少重好過本港"}]}